Back from testing! I nearly broke a leg and my elbow hurts like crap, 
but I think I'm fine. I passed the test with flying colors (or rather 
flying side-kicks), at least I think I did. The results have yet to 
be finalized.

::Killfest/Greven/EndBringer/Demise/Scyther::

Killfest nods. "EndBringer, come with me." He says over his internal 
communication system with his team, "Greven, go to the bridge. 
Scyther, go to the CR room. If no one is there, also go to the 
bridge. Demise, guard Darkmouse, she's too valuable to lose. Violence 
will soon break out, I think you all know how to deal with it."

His team nods and walks out toward the specified positions. Killfest 
opens a comm to DrillBit. "I will meet you in my quarters, room 1468."

He turns a corner, walking to his quarters with EndBringer following 
him. "Darkmouse," he says into his comm, "Report to my quarters as 
soon as you can."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Demise walks to the lab, entering and looking at Darkmouse. "Killfest 
has asigned me to guard you in case the enemy tries to make any 
moves," he says in a raspy voice, one that barely qualified as a 
voice in the first place.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Greven sets off toward the bridge.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Still cloaked and invisible to all sensors, Scyther walks into the CR 
room, looking around.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
